          "content": "At Vanguard Healthcare Solutions, you will work alongside a smart, driven team that goes the extra mile to get the job done right for our patients and physicians. We offer the excitement and opportunity of a fast-growing healthcare company with the stability of an experienced management team, a strong client base, and a proven track record of success.\n\nWe are always looking for people to bring their diverse talents, perspectives and career experiences to help us create the future of healthcare.",
